Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:14.40,White,,0,0,0,,(gemega)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.24,White,,0,0,0,,Una moneda de record.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.52,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.52,White,,0,0,0,,-(dona) Un... un lladre?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:31.32,White,,0,0,0,,U-un lladre!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:33.88,White,,0,0,0,,-(cop: pam)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:33.88,White,,0,0,0,,-Auxili! Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:56.20,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs ara no sé si... On deu ser?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:59.08,White,,0,0,0,,-Ai! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:59.08,White,,0,0,0,,-Surt del mig, bola de greix!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.64,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres, quin mal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:04.40,White,,0,0,0,,M'he fet un nyanyo. Burro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:07.48,White,,0,0,0,,No et deixaré escapar. Espera't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:12.32,White,,0,0,0,,No corris, pocavergonya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:16.88,White,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:19.20,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots dos) Aaaah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:19.20,White,,0,0,0,,-(patacada)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:21.36,White,,0,0,0,,Espera't, no fugis!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:33.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"S'aixeca el teló\Ni apareix el protagonista."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Resol els misteris fent\Nuna dansa preciosa."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:38.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Un lladre topa amb en Genta\Ni no sap el que li espera."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:44.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell\Nd'un adult, i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:47.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Lie, lie, lie, lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:49.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why? Why? Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:52.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Amai uso nara tsuiteite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:02:00.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,Shinjitsu wa setsunaku itai mono DA-KA-RA Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:02.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,Lie, lie, lie, lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:04.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Aimai, my, mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:07.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Isso kimi no subete wo kakete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:11.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,logical na watashi\Nwo damashi nuite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:19.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:23.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kitto hajime wa mujaki na koi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:27.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,eforume shite mita dake soushite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:30.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,Hikari wo matoi yami ni obieru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:33.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,ginmaku sutaa no you ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:41.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sou yo kono mama kyokou no sekai de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:48.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,nazo wo tokeba oikakeru\Nriyuu ga nakunaru wa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:57.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nani mo kamo omoidoori\Nnante tsumaranai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,Lie, lie, lie, lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why? Why? Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Itsuwari demo kamawanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:11.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"El destí encreuat\Nde dues persones".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.92,White,,0,0,0,,És veritat, tens un bon nyanyo.\NQuin mal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:21.80,White,,0,0,0,,Faré el que sigui per trobar aquell home i l'entregaré a la policia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.68,White,,0,0,0,,Nosaltres t'ajudarem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:27.84,White,,0,0,0,,Per cert, Genta, es pot saber\Nquè hi feies, caminant per Oku Beika?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:32.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Doncs, és que...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:32.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Perquè és força lluny de Beika...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:36.24,White,,0,0,0,,Hem de trobar aquell home com sigui\Nsi no volem que se'ns escapi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.72,White,,0,0,0,,Tens raó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Has dit que només l'havies vist\Nper darrere, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.80,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs sí. Portava\Nuna jaqueta vermella i texans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.00,White,,0,0,0,,No és gran cosa,\Nperò què hi farem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:48.04,White,,0,0,0,,(Mitsuhiko) Un moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:48.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Separem-nos i preguntem a la gent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:52.36,White,,0,0,0,,Anomenar-lo "l'agressor de la jaqueta vermella" és molt llarg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.56,White,,0,0,0,,Trobo que li hauríem de buscar\Nun nom en clau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Vols dir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.68,White,,0,0,0,,Un nom en clau?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:58.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:03.60,White,,0,0,0,,Crec que Gonbei seria un bon nom.\NPerquè es fa servir pels desconeguts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Gonbei, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:10.08,White,,0,0,0,,Com que ha fet caure en Genta,\Nli podríem dir Gonta, no trobes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Cada dia t'assembles més\Nal doctor Agasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.84,White,,0,0,0,,Ben pensat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.76,White,,0,0,0,,Ai, ets impressionant.\NÉs un nom fantàstic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.96,White,,0,0,0,,Com que és el Gonbei que ha fet\Ncaure en Genta, li direm Gonta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.44,White,,0,0,0,,És perfecte.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:24.16,White,,0,0,0,,(Genta) És el típic nom\Nque diria el doctor Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.28,White,,0,0,0,,Suposo que això no ho diu\Nper riure's de mi, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:27.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No ho crec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.92,White,,0,0,0,,(gemega)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.24,White,,0,0,0,,Ai, quin mal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:40.12,White,,0,0,0,,És veritat, he caigut d'allà dalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:43.16,White,,0,0,0,,Sí... Per culpa d'aquest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.84,White,,0,0,0,,Però això ara és igual. He de fugir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:50.28,White,,0,0,0,,Un moment...\NPerò si ningú m'ha vist la cara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.60,White,,0,0,0,,Si em canvio la roba...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.36,White,,0,0,0,,"No, no he sigut jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.56,White,,0,0,0,,Algú m'ha canviat la roba\Nmentre estava inconscient".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.16,White,,0,0,0,,"¿Però tu de debò et penses\Nque ens l'empassarem,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.24,White,,0,0,0,,aquesta excusa tan barata?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:11.76,White,,0,0,0,,Que bo! Ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.96,White,,0,0,0,,Res. Ningú ha vist res de res.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Com ha anat, nois?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:23.20,White,,0,0,0,,-Punyeta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:23.20,White,,0,0,0,,-No, ningú.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.44,White,,0,0,0,,On es deu haver ficat,\Naquell poca-solta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.52,White,,0,0,0,,-Ah, sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.52,White,,0,0,0,,-Vols dir en Gonta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.72,White,,0,0,0,,(Takagi) Hola, nois.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:33.24,White,,0,0,0,,Com va, això? Què hi feu, per aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:36.40,White,,0,0,0,,No us heu pas trobat un home\Nsospitós, per casualitat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:39.04,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:39.04,White,,0,0,0,,-Amb jaqueta vermella i texans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:42.08,White,,0,0,0,,És un lladre que acaba de robar\Na casa de la senyora Koda,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:43.96,White,,0,0,0,,una mica més amunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.24,White,,0,0,0,,O sigui que era un lladre, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.60,White,,0,0,0,,-De qui... parleu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:50.84,White,,0,0,0,,Què voleu dir?\NQue l'heu vist, nois?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:54.04,White,,0,0,0,,Sí. Bé, no. De fet,\Nno li he vist la cara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:57.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Quan ha topat amb en Genta i l'ha fet caure a terra, devia fugir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.00,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.00,White,,0,0,0,,-T'ha fet caure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:03.20,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, i mira. M'ha sortit un bon nyanyo\Nal cap i tot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.28,White,,0,0,0,,Per això l'he perseguit una estona.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí, d'acord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Volia entregar-lo a la policia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:11.36,White,,0,0,0,,Les càmeres de prop de l'estació\Nno han detectat cap home
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:13.44,White,,0,0,0,,que encaixi amb la descripció.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.00,White,,0,0,0,,Entesos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:18.68,White,,0,0,0,,Per tant, encara pot estar amagat\Nen algun lloc per aquí a prop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Va.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:22.52,White,,0,0,0,,Ho heu sentit?, ara resulta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:25.20,White,,0,0,0,,que en Gonta no només és violent, sinó també un lladre.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.52,White,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.80,White,,0,0,0,,Hem de fer\Ntot el que puguem per atrapar-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.96,White,,0,0,0,,I ara què fem? S'estan emocionant molt, amb aquest cas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:35.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Tranquil·la... Deu ser un delinqüent\Nque treballa sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però si la cosa es complica,\Ntinc això.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:39.88,White,,0,0,0,,(Mitsuhiko) Conan!\NVa, vinga, anem, de pressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah, sí, ara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.08,White,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:49.48,White,,0,0,0,,-(ocells: piuladissa)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:49.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh..., oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.08,White,,0,0,0,,Ai, ai..., quin mal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:55.88,White,,0,0,0,,Punyeta, no sé ni on soc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:00.12,White,,0,0,0,,No sé com hi he vingut a parar,\Naquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:03.88,White,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ostres..., si no sé qui soc!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:07.08,White,,0,0,0,,Potser... potser porto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.48,White,,0,0,0,,el carnet de conduir, alguna cosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:16.20,White,,0,0,0,,Per què... per què porto això\Na la butxaca?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Disculpi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:23.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Com diu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:23.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Em coneix? Sap qui soc?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:27.48,White,,0,0,0,,No sé què em passa, però no me'n\Nrecordo de qui soc ni d'on vinc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:32.72,White,,0,0,0,,-Doncs no, ni idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:32.72,White,,0,0,0,,-Ostres, noi. No sap ni com es diu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:38.00,White,,0,0,0,,(home: pensa) "Jaqueta vermella\Ni texans."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:40.80,White,,0,0,0,,Oh! Però si resulta\Nque és el lladre que estan buscant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:43.24,White,,0,0,0,,No! Un lladre? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.20,White,,0,0,0,,Vingui, que m'haurà de contestar\Nunes preguntes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.36,White,,0,0,0,,No, no vull que em detinguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.92,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.92,White,,0,0,0,,-Alto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Acabem de trobar en Gonta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.80,White,,0,0,0,,-És ell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:12.08,White,,0,0,0,,És ell, n'estic segur!\NI tant que és en Gonta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:17.64,White,,0,0,0,,Oh! Però què fa entrant a casa meva\Nsense permís?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.16,White,,0,0,0,,És que...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.12,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:31.28,White,,0,0,0,,(semàfor: senyal acústic intermitent)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.80,White,,0,0,0,,(tren: xiulet)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.24,White,,0,0,0,,(home: panteixa)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:47.44,White,,0,0,0,,Per què he comès un robatori?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:51.32,White,,0,0,0,,-(policia: sirena)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:51.32,White,,0,0,0,,-No me'n recordo de res... Per què?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.40,White,,0,0,0,,De totes maneres, si m'atrapen,\Nem tancaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:55.20,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:55.20,White,,0,0,0,,-(vehicle: tanquen la porta)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.48,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! Què fa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.88,White,,0,0,0,,Em roben el cotxe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:04.64,White,,0,0,0,,He de fugir, com sigui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.68,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres... S'ha espatllat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:22.36,White,,0,0,0,,-He de fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:22.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Però què fa?! Alto! Lladre!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:29.12,White,,0,0,0,,Llavors, ¿l'home li ha donat\Nuna empenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.24,White,,0,0,0,,i s'ha emportat la seva bicicleta?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.76,White,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.84,White,,0,0,0,,Primer un cotxe\Ni després una bicicleta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:38.20,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí, i tant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:38.20,White,,0,0,0,,-És dolent dolent, aquest home, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:42.88,White,,0,0,0,,(Mitsuhiko) No serveix de res,\Nque el busquem a l'atzar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:46.04,White,,0,0,0,,(Genta) Potser si anem a la casa\Non ha robat hi trobem alguna cosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.12,White,,0,0,0,,(Ayumi) Sí,\Npotser hi ha alguna pista.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.08,White,,0,0,0,,Hi ha alguna cosa que no veus clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:52.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,L'agent de policia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:55.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,ha dit que semblava\Nque en Gonta tingués amnèsia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:59.20,White,,0,0,0,,Potser si anem a la casa\Non ha robat resoldrem el misteri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.64,Green,,0,0,0,,N'està ben segura,\Nque era un sol home, senyora Koda?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.40,White,,0,0,0,,Del tot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:07.32,White,,0,0,0,,M'ha donat un cop ben fort al cap,\Ndes del darrere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.20,White,,0,0,0,,I quan he tornat en si,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:12.36,White,,0,0,0,,he vist que em robava la moneda\Nde record de l'Exposició de l'Espai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.80,Green,,0,0,0,,L'hi pregunto perquè...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.60,Green,,0,0,0,,a la casa hi ha indicis\Nque hi han entrat dues persones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:21.04,White,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:21.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Només has vist un home, oi, Genta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.20,White,,0,0,0,,També podria ser\Nque la policia s'equivoqués.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.08,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.76,White,,0,0,0,,Ah, hola, nois.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:29.88,White,,0,0,0,,L'inspector Megure m'ha dit\Nque vingués a veure què descobria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:32.76,White,,0,0,0,,Vaja. El senyor Ujihara...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:36.00,White,,0,0,0,,Es diu Masuzo Ujihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:36.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,El coneixes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:38.76,White,,0,0,0,,És un prestador que té el despatx\Ndavant de l'estació de Beika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.84,White,,0,0,0,,Corren rumors que envia gent\Nde dubtosa reputació
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:44.40,White,,0,0,0,,a visitar les persones\Nque no li paguen els deutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:46.48,White,,0,0,0,,Ja fa cara de dolent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Seguim les passes d'en Gonta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:55.64,White,,0,0,0,,(Mitsuhiko) Després de deixar la dona inconscient, ha fugit de la casa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:58.56,White,,0,0,0,,Aquí m'ha donat l'empenta\Ni m'ha fet caure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:02.00,White,,0,0,0,,I més o menys aquí\N'has perdut de vista.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.40,White,,0,0,0,,Què és això?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.48,White,,0,0,0,,Algú ha caigut rodolant, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.80,White,,0,0,0,,Esclar, ja ho tinc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:11.36,White,,0,0,0,,En Gonta anava esverat, ha agafat\Naquest revolt massa de pressa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.44,White,,0,0,0,,i ha caigut daltabaix d'aquest marge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:16.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I aquí és on s'ha donat un cop fort\Nal cap i ha perdut la memòria.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:18.92,White,,0,0,0,,Baixem, de pressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Em sembla que tens raó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:27.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh? Hi ha dues marques...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:30.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Vol dir que han caigut\Ndues persones. Podria ser?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.92,White,,0,0,0,,És veritat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.52,White,,0,0,0,,Això vol dir que hi ha\Nuna altra persona implicada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.60,White,,0,0,0,,Quan en Gonta ha girat la cantonada,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.68,White,,0,0,0,,ha topat amb algú\Nque hi havia per aquí
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.76,White,,0,0,0,,i tots dos han caigut daltabaix.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però és que si fos així...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:46.20,White,,0,0,0,,La persona que ha topat amb ell\Nhauria anat a denunciar-ho, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:49.40,White,,0,0,0,,Però l'inspector Takagi no ha dit\Nque hi hagués cap denúncia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:52.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Exacte. Com és que aquesta persona\Nno ho ha denunciat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja ho tinc!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:57.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No ha dit res perquè encara no sap\Nquè li ha passat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:12:00.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I no ho sap,\Nperquè ha perdut la memòria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.76,White,,0,0,0,,-T'equivoques.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.76,White,,0,0,0,,-Jo no ho veig tan clar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:05.72,White,,0,0,0,,La persona que ha perdut la memòria\Nno és l'home amb qui ha topat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.80,White,,0,0,0,,No, és en Gonta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:10.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:10.56,White,,0,0,0,,Conan, no em diguis que...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:13.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Abans he vist alguna cosa\Nque no encaixava.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:17.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La roba que portava li anava\Nmassa baldera."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:20.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Escolta, Genta,\N¿n'estàs del tot segur,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:23.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que l'home que t'ha donat\Nuna empenta abans era en Gonta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:26.80,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Doncs ara que ho dius, potser...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.52,White,,0,0,0,,En fa l'efecte\Nque era una mica més gros.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:33.68,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs, això ho resol tot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:38.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Han fet un canvi. Després de caure aquí, s'han intercanviat la roba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:41.36,White,,0,0,0,,O sigui que el Gonta\Nque hem buscat fins ara...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:44.24,White,,0,0,0,,Resulta que no és el lladre\Nque m'ha fet caure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:46.92,White,,0,0,0,,Sinó l'home que s'ha vist implicat\Nen l'incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:49.84,White,,0,0,0,,I esclar, ara...,\Ncom que no se'n recorda de res,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:52.36,White,,0,0,0,,es pensa que és un lladre\Ni fuig de la policia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:55.24,White,,0,0,0,,I en realitat ell\Nno havia fet res mal fet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:03.80,White,,0,0,0,,Però per fugir ha acabat fent coses\Ndolentes, i ara el pobre...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.96,White,,0,0,0,,A Beika?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Vinga, nois, tornem a Beika.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.40,White,,0,0,0,,Ho dius pel senyor Ujihara, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:16.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Si aquell home ha obligat el lladre autèntic a cometre el robatori...,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,és normal que hagi aparegut\Na l'escenari del delicte.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:21.32,White,,0,0,0,,Per veure com havia anat tot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:24.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,O perquè estava preocupat\Nper si algú l'havia descobert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:26.72,White,,0,0,0,,És veritat, és molt probable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Si hi parlem, estic segur...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que acabarem trobant\Nel culpable de veritat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.60,White,,0,0,0,,(pensa) "Eh?\NQui són aquests nanos? Oh!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,És al sisè.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.88,White,,0,0,0,,Però com ens ho farem,\Nper parlar-hi, a veure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:52.32,White,,0,0,0,,(pensa) "És aquell nano rodanxó!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "Podria ser...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Mm? Hola, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.48,White,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:08.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I tu què?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:08.44,White,,0,0,0,,Què hi feu, vosaltres, per aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Què hi has vingut a fer, aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.64,White,,0,0,0,,He vingut per parlar\Namb el senyor Masuzo Ujihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.96,White,,0,0,0,,Li vull ensenyar\Naquest retrat robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah, és que...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Aquest home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Ah, inspector Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:22.88,White,,0,0,0,,Veig que els ascensors no funcionen,\No sigui que...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:26.68,White,,0,0,0,,-(Mitsuhiko) Espera't, espera't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:26.68,White,,0,0,0,,-Aquest home no és el lladre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.24,White,,0,0,0,,(pensa) "M'he preocupat per res."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.96,White,,0,0,0,,Miri's bé aquest home, senyor Ujihara, perquè segur que li sona.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.40,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.40,White,,0,0,0,,-El coneix?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:40.72,White,,0,0,0,,Ha-ha! No, jo aquest home\Nno el conec de res.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:44.72,White,,0,0,0,,N'està segur? Perquè\Nquan ha vist el dibuix ha fet... Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:47.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:47.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Espera't un moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.28,White,,0,0,0,,-(porta: es tanca)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.68,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí? Què vols dir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.68,White,,0,0,0,,-Hi ha alguna cosa estranya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:56.24,White,,0,0,0,,Aquest home del retrat robot\Nés una víctima innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.32,White,,0,0,0,,que s'ha vist embolicat en el cas sense voler.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí, de debò?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.64,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots dos) Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.88,White,,0,0,0,,I, tot i així, el senyor Ujihara,\Nquan l'hi ha ensenyat i l'ha vist,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.40,White,,0,0,0,,s'ha posat nerviós.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:08.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Un moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:08.00,White,,0,0,0,,Ho he trobat molt estrany.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:10.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,L'inspector Megure ha dit que...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.64,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja sé què ha passat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:17.40,White,,0,0,0,,Digui'm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.40,White,,0,0,0,,Voldria parlar del robatori d'avui\Na Oku Beika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:24.24,White,,0,0,0,,Sí que sembla que ha sigut ell, sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.36,White,,0,0,0,,Se'n recorda, de mi, oi que sí?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:30.72,White,,0,0,0,,-Aturi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:30.72,White,,0,0,0,,-Ah! Que no s'escapi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.88,White,,0,0,0,,Ah...! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.20,White,,0,0,0,,Ara pagarà per haver-me tirat\Na terra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.40,White,,0,0,0,,-Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.40,White,,0,0,0,,-Iaaah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:43.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Digui?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:43.48,White,,0,0,0,,-(mòbil)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:47.44,White,,0,0,0,,Takagi, soc jo.\NPer fi hem atrapat el sospitós.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:54.04,White,,0,0,0,,És ell, el lladre, segur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:56.16,White,,0,0,0,,Portava aquesta jaqueta vermella\Ni texans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.24,White,,0,0,0,,No, senyora. De fet, no és ell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.76,White,,0,0,0,,(tots dos) Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.76,Green,,0,0,0,,Ah, no? No és ell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.52,White,,0,0,0,,És una història...\Nuna mica complicada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:07.32,White,,0,0,0,,-Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:07.32,White,,0,0,0,,-Senyor Shinya Torimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:09.68,White,,0,0,0,,Ahir vaig sentir una conversa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.52,White,,0,0,0,,entre el senyor Ujihara\Ni un client seu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:17.16,White,,0,0,0,,(Ujihara) A Oku Beika hi viu una dona\Nque es diu Yoshi Koda.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:21.52,White,,0,0,0,,Si tens problemes per cobrar,\Nroba-li alguna cosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:24.92,White,,0,0,0,,M'està dient que cometi un...\Nrobatori?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.88,White,,0,0,0,,Serà fàcil, és una dona gran\Ni viu sola.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.44,White,,0,0,0,,(Torimaru) "Em va semblar una feina fàcil i lucrativa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:35.60,White,,0,0,0,,i avui he entrat a casa seva, aquí."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.48,White,,0,0,0,,"He vist que la dona\Nestava inconscient
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:39.72,White,,0,0,0,,i que algú havia regirat\Ntota la casa."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:42.68,White,,0,0,0,,"Ja que hi era, podia aprofitar\Nper endur-me alguna cosa."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.56,White,,0,0,0,,"I mentre buscava..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.52,White,,0,0,0,,Una moneda de record.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:50.72,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:50.72,White,,0,0,0,,-(dona) Un... un lladre?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:55.00,White,,0,0,0,,-(cop: pam)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:55.00,White,,0,0,0,,-U-un lladre! Auxili!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.28,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs ara no sé si... On deu ser?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:14.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Ai! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:14.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Surt del mig, bola de greix!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.20,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres, quin mal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.32,White,,0,0,0,,-(patacada)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.32,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots dos) Aaaah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.40,White,,0,0,0,,(Genta) Espera't, no fugis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.08,White,,0,0,0,,(gemega)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:31.00,White,,0,0,0,,Oh, quin mal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.72,White,,0,0,0,,És veritat, he caigut d'allà dalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.48,White,,0,0,0,,Sí... Per culpa d'aquest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.24,White,,0,0,0,,Però ara això és igual. He de fugir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.64,White,,0,0,0,,Un moment...\NPerò si ningú m'ha vist la cara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.52,White,,0,0,0,,Si em canvio la roba...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:00.44,White,,0,0,0,,M'he pensat que,\Ncanviant-me la roba amb la seva,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:03.44,White,,0,0,0,,me'n sortiria\Ni li carregarien les culpes a ell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:07.00,White,,0,0,0,,O sigui que resulta que no\Nm'ha agredit un lladre, sinó dos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:10.32,Green,,0,0,0,,Es veu que no treballaven junts...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:10.32,White,,0,0,0,,Sembla mentida!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:13.04,Green,,0,0,0,,Però sí, tots dos\Nhan entrat a casa seva.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:16.36,Green,,0,0,0,,Eh? Doncs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:16.36,White,,0,0,0,,Inspector, això vol dir que ell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:20.64,White,,0,0,0,,Jo no he comès... cap robatori,\Nperò em pensava que sí,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.52,White,,0,0,0,,i mentre fugia he comès\Nun delicte rere l'altre.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.60,White,,0,0,0,,És espantós!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.64,White,,0,0,0,,(plora)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:31.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Senyor Torimaru,\N¿va ser aquesta veu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:34.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,la que va sentir ahir al despatx\Ndel senyor Ujihara?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:38.44,White,,0,0,0,,I ara... I ara què faré?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:43.44,White,,0,0,0,,M'està dient que cometi un robatori?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:45.56,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, i tant, era ell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.64,White,,0,0,0,,Ahir el senyor Ujihara\Nel va amenaçar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:49.32,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots dos) Què?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:49.32,White,,0,0,0,,-Què? A mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:51.88,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, Conan, sembla que tenies raó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:54.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Si el senyor Ujihara\Nno l'hagués empès a robar,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:58.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,no s'hauria posat tan nerviós...\Nquan ha vist el seu retrat robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Exacte.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.76,White,,0,0,0,,O sigui que...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ell ha entrat a robar a casa\Nde la senyora Koda
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i l'ha deixat inconscient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:10.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però mentre buscava coses\Nper robar...,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:13.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,l'ha sentit entrar a vostè\Ni ha decidit fugir corrents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:16.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però, mentre fugia,\Ns'ha torçat el turmell i,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,quan s'ha ajupit per mirar-se'l,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:20.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,vostè ha arribat disparat\Ni ha topat amb ell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:22.16,White,,0,0,0,,Esclar, ara ho entenc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:25.52,Green,,0,0,0,,Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:25.52,White,,0,0,0,,Sembla que tot ha quedat clar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:28.08,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs ara,\Nl'únic que ens queda per fer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:30.88,White,,0,0,0,,és detenir el senyor Ujihara\Nper instigació al robatori.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.76,Green,,0,0,0,,I ja podrem donar aquest cas\Nper resolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:38.20,White,,0,0,0,,He-he-he! O sigui que sí\Nque soc un lladre, en realitat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.64,White,,0,0,0,,Com que el va amenaçar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:42.80,White,,0,0,0,,en Gonta es va veure obligat\Na cometre el robatori.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.92,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Gonta? Jo em dic Gonta?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:48.80,White,,0,0,0,,No. Només és un nom en clau\Nque li hem posat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:51.28,White,,0,0,0,,És veritat, tens raó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:55.28,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots) Gonno Taro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:55.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Em dic Gonta, sí! Gonno Taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:59.84,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, però tothom des de petit\Nem coneix com a... Gonta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:04.88,White,,0,0,0,,Ara me'n recordo de tot.\NJa era hora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.52,White,,0,0,0,,L'empresa on treballava\Nva fer fallida
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:10.72,White,,0,0,0,,i vaig caure en una depressió,\Nperò justament ahir...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.44,White,,0,0,0,,M'està dient\Nque cometi un robatori?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.80,White,,0,0,0,,(Gonta) "Em va sorprendre,\Nperò alhora...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:22.52,White,,0,0,0,,la idea de robar...\Nla vaig trobar emocionant."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.88,White,,0,0,0,,Per això he entrat a la casa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:30.04,White,,0,0,0,,Estava content d'haver trobat\Nun nou objectiu a la meva vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:37.92,White,,0,0,0,,Ha-ha-ha! Però què diu!\NÉs pitjor que jo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:40.24,Green,,0,0,0,,Emporteu-vos aquest parell\Nara mateix!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.12,White,,0,0,0,,Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:48.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Yorisou futari\Nni kimi ga oobaarappu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:53.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ironaki kaze ni omoi hasete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:58.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Fureta te no nukumori ima mo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:03.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Stop jikan wo tomete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:08.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sou itsu no hi datte
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:13.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,kimi no kotoba wasurenai no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:15.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Aitai toki ni aenai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Aitai toki ni aenai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:23.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,Setsunakute modokashii.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:30.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Karakurenai ni somaru togetsukyou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:33.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,michibikareru hi negatte.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:40.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kawa no nagare ni inori wo komete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:45.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:49.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Itsumo kokoro kimi no soba.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:22:00.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:05.64,White,,0,0,0,,Ara que hi penso, què hi feies, tu,\Ncaminant per aquesta zona, Genta?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:08.60,White,,0,0,0,,És veritat,\Nencara no ens ho has explicat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:11.16,White,,0,0,0,,He vingut... ahm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.52,0:22:13.72,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs ara... ara no me'n recordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:16.20,White,,0,0,0,,(tots dos) No pot ser\Nque no te'n recordis!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:18.28,White,,0,0,0,,Quan has caigut t'has donat\Nun cop al cap...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:21.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ha-ha-ha! Doncs sí, és veritat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:23.16,White,,0,0,0,,No me'n recordo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:25.80,White,,0,0,0,,Per què devia venir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:28.12,White,,0,0,0,,(Mitsuhiko) Què?\NEns ho preguntes a nosaltres?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:35.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:35.16,White,,0,0,0,,Fixeu-vos-hi bé, entesos?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:38.40,White,,0,0,0,,Taraaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:40.88,White,,0,0,0,,Aaaah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.40,0:22:45.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,No! Espera, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:50.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "Ostres!\NÉs la botiga on he estat abans!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:55.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No us perdeu el pròxim episodi:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:22:58.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"El punt cec de l'emprovador\N(primera part)".
